---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Caipi">
  <main class="py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8">Last updated: January 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-sm dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-foreground/90">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Overview</h2>
          <p>
            Caipi is designed with privacy in mind. The application runs entirely on your local machine,
            and we collect minimal data necessary to provide and improve our service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Data We Collect</h2>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-foreground mt-6 mb-3">Purchase Information</h3>
          <p>
            When you purchase Caipi, our payment processor Paddle collects:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Email address (for license delivery and support)</li>
            <li>Payment information (processed securely by Paddle)</li>
            <li>Country (for tax compliance)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            This information is subject to <a href="https://www.paddle.com/legal/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline">Paddle's Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-foreground mt-6 mb-3">License Validation</h3>
          <p>
            When you activate your license, we verify it against Paddle's API. This sends:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Your license key</li>
            <li>A device identifier (hashed, non-reversible)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-foreground mt-6 mb-3">Update Checks</h3>
          <p>
            Caipi periodically checks for updates. This sends a request to our update server containing
            only your current version number. No personal information is transmitted.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Data We Do NOT Collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Your conversations with Claude</li>
            <li>Your files or file contents</li>
            <li>Commands you run</li>
            <li>Usage analytics or telemetry</li>
            <li>Browsing history or behavior tracking</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            All interactions with Claude go directly from your device to Anthropic's servers.
            We never see or store this data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-foreground mt-6 mb-3">Anthropic (Claude)</h3>
          <p>
            Caipi uses Claude Code, which connects to Anthropic's servers. Your conversations and
            data sent to Claude are governed by
            <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline">Anthropic's Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-foreground mt-6 mb-3">Paddle</h3>
          <p>
            Payments and license management are handled by Paddle. See
            <a href="https://www.paddle.com/legal/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline">Paddle's Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-foreground mt-6 mb-3">GitHub</h3>
          <p>
            Software updates are distributed via GitHub Releases. See
            <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement" class="text-primary hover:underline">GitHub's Privacy Statement</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
          <p>If you are in the European Union, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
            <li>Data portability</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            To exercise these rights, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:caipi@plpp.de" class="text-primary hover:underline">caipi@plpp.de</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain purchase records and license information for as long as your license is valid
            and for a reasonable period thereafter for legal and accounting purposes. You may request
            deletion of your data at any time.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data.
            All communications use HTTPS encryption. We do not store sensitive payment information —
            this is handled entirely by Paddle.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant
            changes via email or through the Software. Your continued use after changes constitutes
            acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For privacy-related questions or to exercise your rights, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:caipi@plpp.de" class="text-primary hover:underline">caipi@plpp.de</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-primary hover:underline">← Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
